Title: Earn 500 Cube Credits
Notes: Counts credits earned only. Losing credits through buying upgrades, equipment or fuel does not affect progress.

Title: Reach 350 KKM
Notes: Progress updates at the start and end of a jump

Title: Build 5 Cranes
Notes: Progress is tracked at all times, even if the contract is not one of the active 3 (or has already been completed (this is why contract completion sounds keep playing if you build a crane with a pinned completed contract))

Title: Reach 550 KKM
Notes: Progress updates at the start and end of a jump

Title: Raw Amazonite Delivery
Notes: Is only found in underground deposits in MM, underground deposits path

Title: Carbon Fiber Delivery
Notes: Made in Converter from Polymer, manufacturing path

Title: Cracked Ruby Delivery
Notes: Accepts both cracked and flawless Ruby

Title: Cracked Sapphire Delivery
Notes: Accepts both cracked and flawless Sapphire
